Class ModelBundle

java.lang.Object
count.io.ModelBundle
All Implemented Interfaces:
CountXML
public class ModelBundle
extends Object
implements CountXML
Hierarchy data structure for storing a session's members: phylogenies, rate models, and profile tables.
